lead_paragraph: Lindsay Davenport said yesterday that she was considering a return to the WTA Tour. Less than six weeks after giving birth to her son, Jagger, the 31-year-old Davenport was planning to play in a World Team Tennis match Saturday in Sacramento. A gold medalist at the 1996 Olympics, Davenport also said she would like to play in the 2008 Beijing Games.
